com.pedroalmir.athena.core.algorithm
Interface SingularAlgorithm

All Superinterfaces:
Algorithm, java.lang.Cloneable, ConfigurableAlgorithm, java.lang.Runnable, Stoppable
public interface SingularAlgorithm
extends Algorithm, Stoppable, ConfigurableAlgorithm

This class is the abstract base for all algorithms that do not fall within the normal Computational Intelligence type of algorithm.

Examples of such algorithms will include KMeans, Gradient Decent etc.
